thic.<br><br>I mean, how many people could you reasonably interact with in an RP way...50...maybe 100 people - and that would take a lot of typing.  I'm positive that you could find that many to actively roleplay with.<br><br>Just calm down and have fun before you have a stroke or something.<br><br>I've been on the other side of the fence from your opinion, but should you be blessed with the tongue of the celestial felines, I'll rp with you anytime...<br><br>Rexfelix <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 273<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/17/02 12:51:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dear Shintou...</span><hr size=1> I'm not RPing. Don't worry about me IRL. I'm just fine.. Maybe I am venting a little bit, but yes, sometimes the way powergamers try to defend their ways is.. its almost sickening to me.<br><br>But thanks for your concern. I know, I'm walking into the Area of being a bit of an Asshole about it, but man..<br><br>Maybe its just because I just woke up. I hate mornings :/.<br><br>I was trying to refrain from posting again, just say what I had to say and be done with it.<br><br>That didn't happen. It just didn't happen. <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif">Shintou Shinai, A Follower of the Life, and Words of Lanys T'Vyl.Powergamers have EVERY OTHER server out there, maybe even the PvP servers..Can the roleplayers just get ..one?</p><i></i></td>